01:44:00.867 --> 01:44:03.711
- What oil lamps?
- The candles.

01:44:03.770 --> 01:44:07.479
Mom, the groom is coming
to cover my face now.

01:44:07.540 --> 01:44:13.183
- Stop it, baby.
- You can't fool me.

01:44:13.246 --> 01:44:14.919
Feigi, he's coming.

01:44:14.981 --> 01:44:16.392
I'll end up having a stroke.

01:44:16.449 --> 01:44:20.022
Shosh, let's go look for the lamps.

01:44:20.086 --> 01:44:23.329
Give me an update.

01:44:23.389 --> 01:44:25.801
Shimi is the groom.

01:44:25.859 --> 01:44:28.339
Who's Shimi?

01:44:28.394 --> 01:44:30.067
The owner of the hall.

01:44:30.130 --> 01:44:31.666
Remember the lady with the fish
I told you about?

01:44:31.731 --> 01:44:34.439
He's her son.

01:44:34.501 --> 01:44:36.777
How can I help?

01:44:36.836 --> 01:44:40.010
Take off my earrings.

01:44:40.073 --> 01:44:42.883
Okay, it's all taken care of.
Tell me you're okay.

01:44:44.277 --> 01:44:47.087
This must be what drugs
are like, Feigi,

01:44:47.147 --> 01:44:49.718
but way better.

01:44:49.783 --> 01:44:51.228
But pray for me

01:44:51.284 --> 01:44:55.164
that I'll never take this
feeling for granted, okay?

01:44:55.221 --> 01:44:58.498
Neither of us will.

01:45:13.840 --> 01:45:16.411
What is this, Michali?

01:45:18.244 --> 01:45:20.850
The end of the world as we know it,
Mom.

